plot: Nothing is as it seems after Aidan (Brant Daughtery) saves Ronnie (Janel Parrish) from a dangerous encounter. "Something Wicked" is an original horror short that zeroes in on our predisposition of evil and who we become when we face it.
title: Something Wicked
